<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> وَسُئِلَ ابْنُ سِيرِينَ عَنْ الْحِجَارَةِ فِي النَّوْمِ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«قَسْوَةٌ»</span>، وَسُئِلَ عَنِ الْخَشَبِ فِي النَّوْمِ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«نِفَاقٌ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>